imdb.plot outline: The multi-platinum selling rock band deliver a full set of power-pop anthems to a sold-out Atlantic City crowd. Recorded for the premiere episode of HDNet's new concert series 'HD Rock Live,' the show captures thousands of screaming fans singing along to classic GC hits, as well as newer songs off the band's latest release, 'Good Morning Revival.'
